{"tid":675984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個呢刻既感受","createTime":"2018-05-24T04:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T10:05:46.000Z","uid":64624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"39330c6a05c010ae81d52b560e623bcd7b3c0859","tid":675984,"uid":64624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"其實只係想借個平台講下<br />\n<br />\n原來去到感情最後一刻<br />\n先發現自己有幾愛對方同埋自己做得有幾錯<br />\n男人最怕人煩 偏偏我就好煩成日有情緒 <br />\n今次我真係知要點改<br />\n但唔知仲有無機會了<br />\n我真係好希望可以好似以前咁<br />\n<br />\n真係後悔了<br />\n<br />\n大家都可以放底你既感受<br />\n互相鼓勵下<br />\n每個人都值得比人重視同關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30d45a9e52e1c432c5608353cd5c267eef38e76","tid":675984,"uid":165482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:33:38.000Z","msg":"希望天下間所有失信的諾言全部都會實現"},{"pid":"9eebf52874eb65c21777306fef4d876a8dcaa330","tid":675984,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"頹"},{"pid":"1ac48147199a0139d246d26012af482582d5aa0a","tid":675984,"uid":173277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"喊"},{"pid":"f5ca6ebfe14da39676915a0fe86358ce1c7011a1","tid":675984,"uid":173277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"心酸"},{"pid":"1f399e0dec90769a4a31d37dd79d5ae0d2114544","tid":675984,"uid":67610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"好撚柒熱"},{"pid":"d69acc0ca4e5d407e38e7a6285faaf8d797c0be7","tid":675984,"uid":24997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"眼訓"},{"pid":"1f6154eb3fe5eb2690267e6451b34099be31424d","tid":675984,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"寂寞"},{"pid":"df2f8eb52433053f32c098fcf9c09f1a59f83ec9","tid":675984,"uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f6154eb3fe5eb26902